@startuml LCP-UML-4
title Autonomous Vehicle Fleet Network (LCP-UML-4)

' Core vehicle hierarchy
abstract class Vehicle {
  +id: String
  +vin: String
  +status: String
  +location: String
  +updateStatus()
}

abstract class AutonomousVehicle
class GroundVehicle
class AerialVehicle
class SedanAV {
  +version: long
  +lockToken: String
  +updateState(cmd, expectedVersion)
}
class VanAV {
  +version: long
  +lockToken: String
  +updateState(cmd, expectedVersion)
}
class DeliveryDrone {
  +version: long
  +lockToken: String
  +updateState(cmd, expectedVersion)
}

AutonomousVehicle --|> Vehicle
GroundVehicle --|> AutonomousVehicle
AerialVehicle --|> AutonomousVehicle
SedanAV --|> GroundVehicle
VanAV --|> GroundVehicle
DeliveryDrone --|> AerialVehicle

' Power and sensing
class Powertrain
class BatteryPack
class SensorSuite
class LiDARProcessor {
  +version: long
  +lockToken: String
  +refreshPointCloud(expectedVersion)
}
class CameraModule
class RadarModule
class GPSModule

Vehicle *-- Powertrain
Vehicle *-- BatteryPack
Vehicle *-- SensorSuite
SensorSuite *-- LiDARProcessor
SensorSuite *-- CameraModule
SensorSuite *-- RadarModule
SensorSuite *-- GPSModule

' Connectivity and telematics
class ConnectivityModule
class V2XGateway
class VehicleTelematics {
  +collect()
  +compress()
  +send()
}
class TelemetryPacket

Vehicle *-- ConnectivityModule
ConnectivityModule *-- V2XGateway
Vehicle *-- VehicleTelematics
VehicleTelematics *-- TelemetryPacket
V2XGateway --> VehicleTelematics : forwards

' Routing and operations
class RoutePlanner {
  +version: long
  +lockToken: String
  +computeRoute()
  +commitIfVersion(expectedVersion)
}
class MapService
class TrafficService
class ChargingStation {
  +version: long
  +lockToken: String
  +reserveSlot(expectedVersion)
}
class MaintenanceSchedule {
  +beginTx()
  +commitTx()
  +rollbackTx()
}
class IncidentReport {
  +version: long
  +lockToken: String
  +appendEvidence(expectedVersion)
  +beginTx()
  +commitTx()
  +rollbackTx()
}
class RemoteOperatorSupport {
  +takeover()
  +chat()
}

RoutePlanner --> MapService
RoutePlanner --> TrafficService
AutonomousVehicle --> RoutePlanner : requests plan
AutonomousVehicle --> ChargingStation : schedules charge
AutonomousVehicle --> MaintenanceSchedule : sync
AutonomousVehicle --> IncidentReport : files
RemoteOperatorSupport ..> AutonomousVehicle : live control
RemoteOperatorSupport ..> IncidentReport : review

' Passenger booking domain
class PassengerBooking {
  +createBooking()
  +cancel()
  +beginTx()
  +commitTx()
  +rollbackTx()
}
class RideRequest
class PassengerProfile
class PaymentAccount
class TripAssignment {
  +assign()
  +beginTx()
  +commitTx()
  +rollbackTx()
}

PassengerBooking *-- RideRequest
PassengerBooking o-- PassengerProfile
PassengerBooking o-- PaymentAccount
TripAssignment --> PassengerBooking
TripAssignment --> AutonomousVehicle
PassengerBooking --> RoutePlanner : quote ETA

' Data flows to telematics
VehicleTelematics --> IncidentReport : attach evidence
VehicleTelematics --> MaintenanceSchedule : alerts
TelemetryPacket --> RemoteOperatorSupport : live feed

' Additional ground/air relations
BatteryPack --> ChargingStation : charge session
DeliveryDrone --> MapService : geo-fence

' Concurrency and data integrity notes
note right of SedanAV
  Optimistic locking via version + lockToken prevents ghost writes
end note
note right of RoutePlanner
  Route computations commit only when expectedVersion matches; avoids stale overwrites
end note
note right of ChargingStation
  Slot reservations use the same version+token guard to eliminate ghost writes
end note
note right of IncidentReport
  Evidence appends require matching version to prevent duplicate/phantom updates
end note

' ACID & normalization
note as ACID
  Booking, assignment, maintenance and incident workflows run in explicit transactions
  Methods beginTx/commitTx/rollbackTx enforce ACID guarantees
end note
PassengerBooking .. ACID
TripAssignment .. ACID
IncidentReport .. ACID
MaintenanceSchedule .. ACID

note as ThirdNF
  Persistent data model kept in 3NF:
  - Vehicle(id, vin, status, location)
  - RoutePlan(id, vehicle_id, map_ref, traffic_ref)
  - Booking(id, passenger_id, payment_id)
  - TripAssignment(id, booking_id, vehicle_id)
  All non-key attributes depend on the key alone; no transitive dependencies.
end note
Vehicle .. ThirdNF
PassengerBooking .. ThirdNF
TripAssignment .. ThirdNF

@enduml
